'''叶螨科'''（[[學名|學名]]：{{lang|la|'''Tetranychidae'''}}）是[[蛛形綱|蛛形綱]][[蜱蟎亞綱|蜱蟎亞綱]][[真螨目|真螨目]]之下的一個科<ref name="xinjiang">{{cite journal |url=http://www.0x94.com/doc/0MN1cCA5NE4hM5I5U.html |journal=新疆植保学会2012年学术年会 |title=新疆螨类研究进展 |author=[[张建萍|张建萍]] |date=2012-04-07 |accessdate=2016-01-18 |language=zh-hans |location=[[新疆维吾尔自治区|新疆]][[乌鲁木齐市|烏魯木齊]] |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160125231916/http://www.0x94.com/doc/0MN1cCA5NE4hM5I5U.html |archivedate=2016-01-25 }}</ref>。葉蟎科有些物種為害果樹，被泛稱為'''果螨'''，俗称'''红蜘蛛'''或'''黄蜘蛛'''等<ref name="xinjiang" />，皆為[[植食性動物|植食性動物]]，身長從200到900微米不等<ref name="SpiderMitesWeb">{{cite book |first1=Alain |last1=Migeon |first2=Franck |last2=Dorkeld |title=Spider Mites Web: a comprehensive database for the Tetranychidae |url=http://www.montpellier.inra.fr/CBGP/spmweb |language=en |accessdate=2015-01-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091120012222/http://www1.montpellier.inra.fr/CBGP/spmweb/ |archive-date=2009-11-20 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，生活於植物的葉底，紡出具保護作用的絲，也會刺穿植物的細胞來進食<ref name="Saito">{{cite book |author=Yutaka Saito |year=2009 |title=Plant Mites and Sociality: Diversity and Evolution |publisher=[[施普林格科学+商业媒体|Springer]] |isbn=978-4-431-99455-8 |chapter=Plant mites |pages=5–38 |url=http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=dZB5a5FhFgUC&pg=PA11 |doi=10.1007/978-4-431-99456-5_2 |access-date=2016-01-18 |archive-date=2015-04-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150412225559/http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=dZB5a5FhFgUC&pg=PA11 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。由於這個會「紡絲」的特性，葉蟎科在英語也被叫作「[[蛛蟎|蛛蟎]]」。受葉蟎科物種「青睞」的植物有數百個物種。

葉蟎科所屬的[[葉蟎總科|葉蟎總科]]是[[前氣門亞目|前氣門亞目]][[Eleutherengonides|Eleutherengonides]]下目[[Raphignathina|Raphignathina]]小目之下五個總科之一<ref name="Zootaxa">{{cite book |first1=Zhi-Qiang |last1=Zhang |first2=Qing-Hai |last2=Fan |first3=Vladimir |last3=Pesic |first4=Harry |last4=Smit |first5=Andre V. |last5=Bochkov |first6=A. A. |last6=Khaustov |first7=Anne |last7=Baker |first8=Andreas |last8=Wohltmann |first9=Tinghuan |last9=Wen |first10=James W. |last10=Amrine |first11=P. |last11=Beron |first12=Jianzhen |last12=Lin |first13=Grzegorz |last13=Gabrys |first14=Robert |last14=Husband |chapter=Order '''Trombidiformes''' <small>Reuter, 1909</small> |chapterurl=http://www.mapress.com/zootaxa/2011/f/zt03148p138.pdf |url=http://www.mapress.com/zootaxa/list/2011/3148.html |title=Animal biodiversity: An outline of higher-level classification and survey of taxonomic richness |editor=Zhang, Z.-Q. |journal=[[Zootaxa|Zootaxa]] |issue=3148 |year=2011 |pages=133 |publisher=[[Magnolia_Press|Magnolia Press]] |isbn=9781869778491 |language=en |access-date=2016-01-18 |archive-date=2015-12-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151222175509/http://www.mapress.com/zootaxa/list/2011/3148.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。本科的物種有95個屬<ref name="Zootaxa" />、約1200個物種<ref>{{cite book |author=H. R. Bolland, Jean Gutierrez & Carlos H. W. Flechtmann |year=1997 |title=World Catalogue of the Spider Mite Family (Acari: Tetranychidae) |publisher=[[Brill_Publishers|Brill Publishers]] |isbn=978-90-04-11087-8 |chapter=Introduction |pages=1–3 |url=http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=OALu9cfevl8C&pg=PA1 |access-date=2016-01-18 |archive-date=2015-04-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150427111313/http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=OALu9cfevl8C&pg=PA1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>（準確來說，有1288個物種<ref name="SpiderMitesWeb" />）。由於物種眾多，一般會再細分為兩大亞科（[[苔蟎亞科|苔蟎亞科]]跟[[葉蟎亞科|葉蟎亞科]]）和多個族。

阿逼古斯<ref name="Saito"/>。

==生命週期==
[[File:Tetranychidae.jpg|thumb]]上生活的葉蟎]]
炎熱和乾燥的環境經常都與葉蟎數量增加有關連。在最佳條件（約{{convert|80|F|C|disp=or}}）之下，[[二斑葉蟎|二斑葉蟎]]可以在短短的三天內孵化，在五天內達至[[性成熟|性成熟]]。
一個雌蟲產卵可達每天20顆，所以在其2週〜4週的生命裡，合共可產下數百顆蟲卵。
這加快了的繁殖率，讓葉蟎科種群可以迅速適應抵禦[[殺蟲劑|殺蟲劑]]，使化學防治方法在長久使用會變得無效<ref name="IFAS"/>。

[[产雄孤雌生殖|产雄孤雌生殖]]現像<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.iciba.com/%E4%BA%A7%E9%9B%84%E5%AD%A4%E9%9B%8C%E7%94%9F%E6%AE%96 |title=产雄孤雌生殖 |language=zh-hans |accessdate=2016-01-19 }}</ref>（Arrhenotoky，一種[[孤雌生殖|孤雌生殖]]的特例）現像在葉蟎科物種亦有出現，就好像[[膜翅目|膜翅目]]物種或一些[[介殼蟲|介殼蟲]]那樣：雌性物種的染色體是[[二倍體|二倍體]]，而雄性物種的卻是[[單倍體|單倍體]]<ref name="Bell1982">{{cite book |author=Graham Bell |year=1982 |title=The Masterpiece of Nature: the Evolution and Genetics of Sexuality |series=Croom Helm applied biology series |publisher=[[劍橋大學出版社|Cambridge University Press]] |isbn=978-0-85664-753-6 |url=http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=q5g9AAAAIAAJ&pg=PA238 |chapter=Parthenogenesis and vegetative reproduction in multicellular animals |pages=160–331 |access-date=2016-01-18 |archive-date=2014-09-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140912004040/http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=q5g9AAAAIAAJ&pg=PA238 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
當交配時，雌性會避免令一些卵子受精，以產生雄性物種。受精卵只會產生二倍體的雌性；而未交配及未受精的雌性物種仍然可以產卵，使產下的全部都是單倍體的雄性。

