[[二斑叶螨|二斑叶螨]]（''[[二斑叶螨|Tetranychus urticae]]''）是本科物種中最為知名的，除了其[[世界性分佈|世界性分佈]]<ref name="Raworth">{{cite book |editor=Peter G. Mason & John Theodore Huber |year=2002 |title=Biological Control Programmes in Canada, 1981–2000 |publisher=[[CAB_International|CAB International]] |isbn=978-0-85199-527-4 |author=D. A. Raworth, D. R. Gillespie, M. Roy & H. M. A. Thistlewood |chapter=''Tetranychus urticae'' Koch, twospotted spider mite (Acari: Tetranychidae) |pages=259–265 |url=http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=tDHWhOEhTckC&pg=PA259 |access-date=2016-01-18 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307113251/https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=tDHWhOEhTckC&pg=PA259 |dead-url=no }}</ref>之外，牠們還會對很多不同種類的植物攻擊，包括有一般昆蟲討厭的[[辣椒|辣椒]]、[[番茄|番茄]]、[[馬鈴薯|馬鈴薯]]、[[豆類|豆類]]、[[玉米|玉米]]、[[大麻|大麻]]、[[草莓|草莓]]等<ref name="IFAS">{{cite web |url=http://entomology.ifas.ufl.edu/creatures/orn/twospotted_mite.htm |title=Twospotted spider mite |publisher=[[佛罗里达大学|University of Florida]] / [[Institute_of_Food_and_Agricultural_Sciences|Institute of Food and Agricultural Sciences]] |work=Featured Creatures |accessdate=2011-05-20 |date=2009-12 |first1=Thomas R. |last1=Fasulo |first2=H. A. |last2=Denmark |language=en |archive-date=2012-11-22 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6CNGRkAeM?url=http://entomology.ifas.ufl.edu/creatures/orn/twospotted_mite.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。其他在經濟上影響比較重要的害蟲有[[蘋果全爪蟎|蘋果全爪蟎]]（''[[Panonychus_ulmi|Panonychus ulmi]]''）和[[柑桔全爪蟎|柑桔全爪蟎]]（''[[Panonychus_citri|Panonychus citri]]''）。

